      "title": "Iron-sulfur clusters: ever-expanding roles",
      "abstract": "Iron-sulfur clusters have critical roles in proteins from diverse organisms and in a broad range of biological processes. Recent discoveries raise exciting challenges for future research by bioinorganic chemists and chemical biologists."
